rComments: Francis was a great professor. Learning a language is very difficult for anyone and it is clear he knows this and has no issue taking the time to help any of us students learn. I highly recommend taking courses with him as he is hilarious and very helpful. Participation is important here because it is a language after all - you must be able tospeak
